        "subject": "LU-14509 ptlrpc: Close request can't be sent",
        "message": "LU-14509 ptlrpc: Close request can't be sent\n\nThere is a slot for close request but close\nthread can't be woken up due to exclusive wait.\n\nMake close wait as non-exclusive, so it will be\nwoken up with each call.\n\nChange-Id: I4d24814db360e49612c09c9899b33d1a39037763\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-9344\nFixes: 7fa0fd4157 (\"LU-11441 obdclass: make mod rpc slot wait queue FIFO\")\nSigned-off-by: Andriy Skulysh <c17819@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Vitaly Fertman <c17818@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Vladimir Saveliev <c17830@cray.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
